          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='33625' id='19' type-v2='text' w='45900' x='51400' y='57875'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#0e101a' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='12'>Key Points:</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#0e101a' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='12'>- Infant care is the priciest type of childcare with average prices for this type of   care exceeding those for toddler care and preschool care in most states.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#0e101a' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='12'>- Prices for childcare services vary greatly across the United States, with the District of Columbia &amp; Massachusetts having significantly higher prices than other states.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#0e101a' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='12'>- Higher-income areas have significantly higher prices for childcare, indicating a moderate relationship between regional income levels and prices for childcare.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
